    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Sigma Squad is a fast-paced, competitive multiplayer FPS that takes the classic genre experience to a new level of precision.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >“What you see is what you get,” some say. In Sigma Squad, we have that too, but with one difference—it actually works here. With 256-tickrate servers, we guarantee smooth gameplay and precise shots that let you trust every move you make.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3249210/extras/9e63d4c3a3cfa4141c7cdddeb70a44c6.poster.avif?t=1733400661\" width=800 height=156 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3249210/extras/9e63d4c3a3cfa4141c7cdddeb70a44c6.webm?t=1733400661\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3249210/extras/9e63d4c3a3cfa4141c7cdddeb70a44c6.mp4?t=1733400661\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore five unique maps, each inspired by different cultures and iconic spots:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Freedom Land</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Maiameee</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hong</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Japanese Sunset</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >&quot;The day&quot;</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Created by a small, family-run indie studio with over 10 years of experience in technology development, <i>Sigma Squad</i> represents our passion for the genre and our desire to deliver an enhanced and precise experience for both casual and competitive players alike.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >We greatly appreciate your support in adding Sigma Squad to your wishlist.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3249210/extras/575c9453add34b4b8a3bb1c3bdf01417.avif?t=1733400661\" width=800 height=417 /></span></p>",
